title: Kiss Woman Person Medium Light Skin Tone No Skin Tone
description: Represents a romantic kiss between a woman and a man, with both individuals having a medium-light skin tone.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji portrays a woman’s face with a gentle, closed-mouth smile and closed eyes, conveying a sweet and affectionate kiss. The medium-light skin tone is rendered with Apple's signature soft gradients and subtle highlights, giving it a warm, realistic glow.  The smooth, rounded edges of the facial features and the subtle 3D shading contribute to its tender and loving expression, perfect for sending a kiss or expressing fondness in your digital conversations on Apple devices.
